  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary aim of this report is to determine whether there is a difference between&#xD;
      Epinephrine and Tranexamic acid in providing visual clarity during arthroscopic rotator cuff&#xD;
      tear repair.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
